Hi,

Thanks for writing to Dr. Math.

1% of 1281.16 is 12.8116. So, 1.99% should be close to twice 12.8116
or 25.62. So, $25.50 sounds much closer to the true value. 

Does this help?  Please feel free to write back with any questions you
may have.

